snippet.title: These ACTORS will REPLACE Amber Heard in AQUAMAN 2! | OG CELEBRITY
snippet.description:
These Actors will Replace Amber Heard in Aquaman 2! 
The majority of people feel that Zack Snyder's Justice League exists just to increase the number of HBO Max subscribers. Although 70 million dollars for a remake of a failed film may appear to be a hefty number, Netflix and Disney have regularly spent more on exclusive streaming content. Amber Heard's absence from all DC films is discussed by Zack Snyder. Indeed, if Warner Bros. had been sold on Snyder's original vision, he would not have had Joss Whedon reshoot 95% of the picture after Snyder had departed.
